eports `fails-native-image-run`, compare the exact CI branch/environment against the current tree, because the preserved/generated native test output is already passing.\n3. If this remains non-reproducible after fixing the agent environment, reclassify the issue as infrastructure/tooling failure rather than a metadata defect for this library."}}
